  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-badge">Open Source &middot; Self-Hosted &middot; Docker</span>
      <h1>Your phone system.<br/><span>Modern management.</span></h1>
      <p>
        GonoPBX is a web-based management interface for Asterisk &ndash;
        a side project that grows step by step.
        Extensions, SIP trunks, call forwarding, voicemail, and call history &ndash;
        all via an intuitive web GUI. The project is still evolving and
        I am always open to new ideas &ndash; if you have a suggestion,
        feel free to reach out. I will implement it as time allows.
      </p>
